# Spotify Web API (optional — for starting playback from the UI/agent, metadata and search).
# Create an app at https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
#   - API: Web API
#   - Redirect URI: http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/spotify/callback
# Then copy this file to .env and fill in the values.
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=
